item.title: Need loads of help lol
item.dc:creator: @M_A_R_T_Y M A R T Y
item.description:
@M_A_R_T_Y wrote:

changing starting point - Go to player.java and look for something like this:

// initial x and y coordinates of the player heightLevel = 0; // the first call to updateThisPlayerMovement() will craft the proper initialization packet teleportToX = 2577; // 2576; teleportToY = 3299; // 3299

Just change the cords to where you want your starting point to be.

No runes needed for magic - i have no idea

Changing what it says in quest tab - Just go to client.java and then look in your server and see what it currently says in quest tab, then click ctrl+f type in what it says and then replace it with what you want

Compile after doing everything
